chess.domain.pieces

Class Piece

  • java.lang.Object
    • chess.domain.pieces.Piece
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bishop, King, Knight, Pawn, Queen, Rook

    public abstract class Piece
extends Object
    This is an abstract parent class of all chess pieces containing information of its location and owner. This class also offers methods to access that knowledge.
    Author:
    sami
